WEBVTT

00:00.047 --> 00:03.346
- Previously on Game of Silence...
- How you doing, little brother?

00:03.500 --> 00:04.530
I just heard about Darryl.

00:04.540 --> 00:05.893
- What happened?
- Goes back to Quitman.

00:06.573 --> 00:07.540
Quitman?

00:07.540 --> 00:09.101
TERRY: Those kids from the riot.
Little kid Boots,

00:09.111 --> 00:10.460
he sees Darryl in the streets,

00:10.460 --> 00:11.580
he hits him, so I hit back.

00:11.580 --> 00:13.490
Mr. Nolan was represented by a lawyer

00:13.500 --> 00:15.058
named Jackson Brooks.

00:15.068 --> 00:16.712
Jackson.

00:17.335 --> 00:19.965
We build a case, brick by brick,

00:19.975 --> 00:22.122
solid as a rock, and
then we put 'em away.

00:22.132 --> 00:24.004
Bobby, why don't you go on record?

00:24.004 --> 00:26.241
- We got a witness.
- He went on camera

00:26.251 --> 00:28.580
- and he told us everything he saw.
- Bobby, no!

00:28.580 --> 00:31.420
SHAWN: He said the last person he
saw Petey with was the warden.

00:31.420 --> 00:32.490
BOBBY: I wish I could've

00:32.500 --> 00:34.131
- done something else.
- Bravo.

00:34.141 --> 00:35.610
You blamed everybody but yourself.

00:35.620 --> 00:37.550
Poor little Bobby, just doing his job!

00:37.560 --> 00:38.590
The guy's a liar.

00:38.590 --> 00:39.580
How do you know? 'Cause he said

00:39.590 --> 00:41.003
he wasn't at the warden's parties.

00:41.028 --> 00:42.503
You got somewhere to keep this camera?

00:42.528 --> 00:43.595
You gonna leave it with me?

00:43.620 --> 00:45.399
Yeah, I'm gonna leave it with you.
I trust you.

00:45.408 --> 00:46.630
I had some visitors today.

00:46.630 --> 00:47.801
Some of those boys from Quitman.

00:47.801 --> 00:49.620
I just thought you should know.

00:54.510 --> 00:57.460
(siren wailing and dog barking
in distance)

